    description: "Botox injected into the soft palate and pharyngeal muscles is an emerging treatment for snoring and mild sleep apnea in men. Clinical evidence is promising — though it is not a replacement for a formal sleep apnea workup. Here is what the research says, how it compares to other options, and whether you are a candidate.",
